title: David and Goliath. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: April 3rd, 2015

Description:

Filmed in North Africa and London, David and Goliath looks at one of the most powerful and beloved Bible stories of all time. The epic film focuses on the early life of David, who fought against the Philistine giant Goliath against all odds.

Director: Tim Chey

Writers: Tim Chey

Actors: Miles Sloman, Jerry Sokolosky, Makenna Guyler, Joseph Emms, Paul Hughes, Simon Davies, Richard Summers-Calvert, Jared Morgan, Tom Bonington, Juju Ballo

Genre: Drama, Thriller

Run Time: 1 hour 32 minutes
